WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:01.902
Head uudised:

00:00:01.902 --> 00:00:03.707
selleks pole terminali vaja!

00:00:03.707 --> 00:00:06.413
Avame täieliku VS Code otse brauseris,

00:00:06.413 --> 00:00:07.767
loome mõned failid,

00:00:07.767 --> 00:00:10.022
käivitame mõned käsud ja vaatame,

00:00:10.022 --> 00:00:12.729
kuidas kernel kõik repo sees hoiab.

00:00:13.503 --> 00:00:14.970
Idee on selline.

00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:17.415
Editor ei tööta sinu sülearvutis.

00:00:17.415 --> 00:00:20.348
See töötab serveri repo sandbox'is ja

00:00:20.348 --> 00:00:23.282
sinu brauser jõuab selleni SSH-tunneli kaudu.

00:00:23.282 --> 00:00:24.749
Nii näevad failipuu,

00:00:24.749 --> 00:00:26.705
sisseehitatud terminal ja kõik,

00:00:26.705 --> 00:00:28.172
mida sealt käivitad,

00:00:28.172 --> 00:00:29.150
täpselt seda,

00:00:29.150 --> 00:00:30.617
mida repo näeb,

00:00:30.617 --> 00:00:32.572
ja mitte midagi muud.

00:00:35.843 --> 00:00:36.613
One command.

00:00:36.613 --> 00:00:39.309
The CLI installs the editor server on

00:00:39.309 --> 00:00:40.464
the machine once,

00:00:40.464 --> 00:00:42.775
starts it inside the repo sandbox,

00:00:42.775 --> 00:00:43.931
opens a tunnel,

00:00:43.931 --> 00:00:45.856
and hands you a link.

00:00:45.856 --> 00:00:47.397
No local VS Code,

00:00:47.397 --> 00:00:49.322
no extensions to set up.

00:00:52.322 --> 00:00:54.739
See URL on sinu redaktor.

00:00:54.739 --> 00:00:56.188
Töötab igal opsüsteemil,

00:00:56.188 --> 00:00:58.121
ainus nõue on brauser.

00:00:58.647 --> 00:01:00.338
Ja siin ta on:

00:01:00.338 --> 00:01:01.184
VS Code,

00:01:01.184 --> 00:01:02.030
brauseri vahekaardil.

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:04.567
Vasakul olev failipuu näitab repot ja

00:01:04.567 --> 00:01:05.413
ainult repot.

00:01:11.147 --> 00:01:12.779
Loome päris faili,

00:01:12.779 --> 00:01:14.411
terminali pole vaja.

00:01:14.411 --> 00:01:15.499
Uus redaktor,

00:01:15.499 --> 00:01:18.219
paar rida ja salvestame selle

00:01:18.219 --> 00:01:19.851
notes/todo.md nime alla.

00:01:19.851 --> 00:01:21.484
Kaust ilmub vasakule,

00:01:21.484 --> 00:01:23.660
kui fail repo'sse jõuab.

00:01:29.647 --> 00:01:32.604
Sisseehitatud terminal töötab samuti ja siin

00:01:32.604 --> 00:01:34.082
on meie fail.

00:01:34.082 --> 00:01:36.546
Nüüd proovime repost välja vaadata:

00:01:36.546 --> 00:01:37.531
juurdepääs keelatud.

00:01:37.531 --> 00:01:39.010
See pole seadistus,

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:40.488
see on kernel.

00:01:48.647 --> 00:01:50.685
Same repo from the plain terminal:

00:01:50.685 --> 00:01:52.722
the working directory is the repo,

00:01:52.722 --> 00:01:54.760
the files are the repo's files.

00:01:57.563 --> 00:02:00.087
Terminal ja redaktor on ühel meelel,

00:02:00.087 --> 00:02:01.769
see on sama sandbox.

00:02:05.033 --> 00:02:07.602
And the file we created in the

00:02:07.602 --> 00:02:08.336
browser editor?

00:02:08.336 --> 00:02:09.070
Right here.

00:02:09.070 --> 00:02:11.638
Files made in VS Code are real

00:02:11.638 --> 00:02:12.372
repo files,

00:02:12.372 --> 00:02:12.739
instantly.

00:02:14.489 --> 00:02:15.678
Loodud brauseris,

00:02:15.678 --> 00:02:16.866
loetav terminalist.

00:02:16.866 --> 00:02:18.055
Üks repo,

00:02:18.055 --> 00:02:19.243
kaks ust.

00:02:22.576 --> 00:02:24.184
Now try to leave.

00:02:24.184 --> 00:02:26.595
Listing the root of the server:

00:02:26.595 --> 00:02:27.399
permission denied.

00:02:27.399 --> 00:02:29.408
The kernel scopes the editor,

00:02:29.408 --> 00:02:30.212
its terminal,

00:02:30.212 --> 00:02:33.025
and every child process to this repo.

00:02:34.775 --> 00:02:36.473
Keelatud kerneli poolt,

00:02:36.473 --> 00:02:38.171
mitte konfiguratsiooni poolt.

00:02:41.482 --> 00:02:42.949
Other users' homes?

00:02:42.949 --> 00:02:43.926
Also denied.

00:02:43.926 --> 00:02:46.859
Whatever runs inside this sandbox —

00:02:46.859 --> 00:02:47.348
editors,

00:02:47.348 --> 00:02:47.837
terminals,

00:02:47.837 --> 00:02:50.770
build tools — ends at the

00:02:50.770 --> 00:02:51.748
repo's walls.

00:02:53.498 --> 00:02:55.196
Sandboxil pole erandeid.

00:02:55.196 --> 00:02:56.894
See ongi mõte.

00:02:57.688 --> 00:02:58.273
Brauser,

00:02:58.273 --> 00:02:58.858
editor,

00:02:58.858 --> 00:02:59.443
terminal:

00:02:59.443 --> 00:03:00.612
sama sandbox,

00:03:00.612 --> 00:03:01.782
samad reeglid.

00:03:01.782 --> 00:03:03.537
Järgmisena tuleb funktsioon,

00:03:03.537 --> 00:03:05.876
millele kõik siin põhineb,

00:03:05.876 --> 00:03:06.461
forking.

00:03:06.461 --> 00:03:08.215
Sulle meeldib see.
